body:
I met with a similar problem like this. Try using `graph_transform` instead of `quantize_graph`
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/master/tensorflow/tools/graph_transforms

Be sure to use `quantize_weights` and `quantize_nodes` successively in the command for graph transform.
